data.description: Great home in Valley Ranch, this 5 bedroom and 3.5 bathroom offers an open floor plan for both entertaining and everyday living. The master suite is a great size, This home boasts an extended patio. Valley Ranch is known for its highly sought-after location, with easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. With its close proximity to major highways, commuting to work or exploring the surrounding areas is a breeze. Enjoy access to a clubhouse, perfect for hosting events and gatherings. Stay active and fit with the on-site gym, or take a refreshing dip in the pools with water slides. If you love the outdoors, you'll appreciate the playground and walking trails that wind through the neighborhood, providing a serene setting for a leisurely stroll or jog.
